Description
This gorgeous yarn is very similar to Wolles Color Changing Yarn in that it is 4 strands of unplyed yarn with each colour change taking place one strand at a time. This allows for a very long and gradual colour change as you knit. The yarn also comes with a free pattern for the Mariner shawl shown in the picture.
All the colours wouldn’t fit on 1 page so here is the link to the 2nd page of colours!
100% Cotton Gradient Yarn / Fingering Weight / 480 yards / 130 grams
3.75 mm needle is recommended
Made in Merrickville, Ontario Canada


Additional information


Weight
130 g


Colour
